    {
      "type": "text",
      "tag": "p",
      "text": "My mission is to rebrand, modernize, and lower both the learning and re-learning cost of the U Serve interface. POS interfaces are conventionally text-dense and have a flat information architecture. The goal is to achieve a balance between aesthetics and functional efficiency, ensuring a smooth transition for all users."
