    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Specs for Dev Team"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "tag": "p",
      "text": "Considering the varying screen sizes of POS tablets, I defined the specifications for a responsive design to assist our development team in implementing it effectively."
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/63a0d533a7afeac89489815e/697aeb724d25cda58b27bca5_Design%20System-p-1600.png",
      "alt": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/63a0d533a7afeac89489815e/66d51d61e232491615b8e5af_Screen%20Shot%202024-09-01%20at%2010.04.46%20PM.png",
      "alt": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Reflections"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "tag": "p",
      "text": "I am grateful to Universal Processing LLC for giving me this internship opportunity. It has been an invaluable experience designing for systems with unique structures and an extensive user coverage. Over the past few months, I have learned to communicate more effectively with the development team through:"
    },
    {
      "type": "listItem",
      "tag": "li",
      "text": "Providing detailed specifications for responsive design, including different breakpoints and layout adjustments for various screen sizes."
    },
    {
      "type": "listItem",
      "tag": "li",
      "text": "Asking and understanding the technical feasibility of design elements and adjust designs accordingly."
    },
    {
      "type": "listItem",
      "tag": "li",
      "text": "Identifying as many edge cases as possible to ensure the design accommodates a wide range of scenarios and user interactions."
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "tag": "p",
      "text": "‍I also enhanced my UIUX skills in how to :"
    },
    {
      "type": "listItem",
      "tag": "li",
      "text": "Represent complicate data relationships by using multi-status elements, layered levels with independent affordances, parallel and sequential processes, and accounting information."
    },
    {
      "type": "listItem",
      "tag": "li",
      "text": "Prioritize features and employ design tactics to manage space efficiently, ensuring a clean and functional layout."
    },
