    {
      "level": 1,
      "heading": "Specs for Dev Team",
      "content": [
        "Considering the varying screen sizes of POS tablets, I defined the specifications for a responsive design to assist our development team in implementing it effectively."
      ],
      "media": [
        {
          "type": "image",
          "src": "https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/63a0d533a7afeac89489815e/697aeb724d25cda58b27bca5_Design%20System-p-1600.png",
